# Project Dashboard CopilotKit - Phase Report

This document compiles the architectural insights, dependency audits, and flow mapping conducted across all phases of the dashboard-copilotkit project.

## Phase 01: Baseline Architecture & Flow Mapping

**Goal:** Establish a verified baseline of the current architecture, tech stack, and end-to-end data flows.

### Findings
- **Automated Mapping:** Baseline architecture established via static analysis (`knip`, `dependency-cruiser`).
- **Data Flow:** E2E dashboard data fetch flow documented and traced.
- **Idiomatic Assessment:** Assessed React 19 and NestJS 11 usage within the monorepo.

### Artifacts
- `baseline-architecture.dot`: System dependency graph.
- `e2e-flow.mermaid`: End-to-end data flow diagram.
- `idiomatic-assessment.md`: Framework usage evaluation.

